'''性慾亢進'''（{{lang-en|Hypersexuality}}）是[[精神衛生|精神衛生]]研究人員和精神衛生機構所使用的[[诊断|臨床診斷]]，去形容極為頻繁或突然增加的[[性衝動|性衝動]]或[[性活動|性活動]]。[[女性|女性]]患上此病叫Nymphomania{{#tag:ref|学名：花痴症，俗称：花痴、花癫者{{r|nownews}}{{r|zgxkx201103}}|group=注}}{{r|zgxkx201103}}。[[男性|男性]]患上這種疾病被稱為Satyriasis{{#tag:ref|学名：求雌狂、男性色情狂、俗称：色鬼。{{r|zgxkx201103}}|group=注}}，名稱來自[[寧芙|寧芙]]及[[薩堤爾|薩堤爾]]{{r|zgxkx201103}}，但在一般醫療人員中不再使用。

==用语==
韋氏詞典定義性慾亢進「在性活動中表現出異常或過度的關切/沉溺」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/hypersexual|title=Hypersexual – Definition of hypersexual by Merriam-Webster|work=merriam-webster.com|access-date=2016-08-18|archive-date=2019-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524071920/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/hypersexual|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自19世紀後期，當[[理查德·冯·克拉夫特-埃宾|理查德·冯·克拉夫特-埃宾]]於1886年出版描述極端性行為的開創性書籍《性病態》，性學家一直在使用「性慾亢進」這個詞<ref>Krafft-Ebing, R. von (1886/1965). ''Psychopathia sexualis: A medico–forensic study'' (H. E. Wedeck, Trans.). New York: Putnam.</ref><ref name=Kafka2010>[[Martin_Kafka|Kafka, M. P.]] (2010). [http://www.dsm5.org/Documents/Sex%20and%20GID%20Lit%20Reviews/Paraphilias/KAFKAHD.pdf Hypersexual Disorder: A proposed diagnosis for DSM-V] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dsm5.org/Documents/Sex%20and%20GID%20Lit%20Reviews/Paraphilias/KAFKAHD.pdf |date=20120914110342 }}. ''Archives of Sexual Behavior, 39,'' 377–400.</ref>。作者在當時使用「性慾亢進」描述現在被稱為「[[早洩|早洩]]」的狀況。[[男性|男性]]患上這種疾病被稱為「donjuanist」<ref>{{cite book|last1=Sifuentes-Jáuregui|first1=B|title=Transvestism, Masculinity, and Latin American Literature: Genders Share Flesh|date=2002|page=207}}</ref> 、「satyromaniac」<ref>{{cite book|last1=Scruton|first1=Roger|title=Sexual Desire: A Philosophical Investigation|date=2015|page=168}}</ref> 、「Satyriasis」<ref>{{cite book|last1=Spooner|first1=Henry|title=American Journal of Urology and Sexology|date=1918|page=565}}</ref>(学名：男性色情狂)；[[女性|女性]]則叫Nymphomania(学名：花痴症)<ref>{{cite book|last1=Nemerof|first1=Charles|title=The Concise Corsini Encyclopedia of Psychology and Behavioral Science|date=2004|page=630}}</ref>；性慾亢進患者(hypersexualist)則是較为中性的用语<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.nationalpost.com/full-comment/jen-gerson-feel-free-to-opt-for-the-epidural-sans-guilt-new-moms |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-08-18 |archive-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006082622/http://news.nationalpost.com/full-comment/jen-gerson-feel-free-to-opt-for-the-epidural-sans-guilt-new-moms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
==概要==
性慾亢進可能是首要的病況，或另一疾病或病況的症狀，如[[克魯爾-布西症候群|克魯爾 - 布西症候群]]或[[躁鬱症|躁鬱症]]。性慾亢進還可能是藥物的副作用所致，如用於治療[[帕金森氏病|帕金森氏病]]的藥物，或施用荷爾蒙(如[[睾丸激素|睾丸激素]]和[[雌激素|雌激素]])所引起的效果。臨床醫師還沒有達成對如何最好地形容性慾亢進為首要病況的共識<ref>Stein, D. J. (2008). Classifying hypersexual disorders: Compulsive, impulsive, and addictive models. ''Psychiatric Clinics of North America, 31,'' 587–592.</ref><ref>Bancroft, J., & Vukadinovic, Z. (2004). [http://66.199.228.237/boundary/Sexual_Addiction/sexual_addiction_sexual_compulsivity_sexual_impulsivity_or_what_toward_a_theoretical_model.pdf Sexual addiction, sexual compulsivity, sexual impulsivity or what? Toward a theoretical model] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205020328/http://66.199.228.237/boundary/Sexual_Addiction/sexual_addiction_sexual_compulsivity_sexual_impulsivity_or_what_toward_a_theoretical_model.pdf |date=2014-12-05 }}. ''[[Journal_of_Sex_Research|Journal of Sex Research]]'', 41, 225–234.</ref><ref>
